-- Delhi Commonwealth Games Stadiums Won't Be Ready by Deadline, Times Says
-- Saikat Chatterjee
-- 2010-07-21T03:14:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/delhi-commonwealth-games-stadiums-won-t-be-ready-by-deadline-times-says.html

          
          
             The organizers of the October
Commonwealth Games in New Delhi won’t have stadiums ready by the
Aug. 1 deadline, the Times of India reported, citing officials
it didn’t identify.  
 Work on the main stadium and accompanying projects such as
approach roads and landscaping will remain unfinished during the
handover to the organizing committee, the newspaper said.  
